setting up hosting a static web site hosting using s3 bucket 
add cloudfront distriubution which uses edge location and serves the requests using cached content
we can set up authentication from cdn to s3 using origin access control
lly, we can authorize CDN using s3 bucket policy to copy or fetch content from s3 bucket to edge locations.
additionally, we can use r53 and route the domain to cdn fqdn
also, we can use certificate manager to use https for secure access